snippet.title: Robot Roller-Derby Disco Dodgeball - Official Launch Trailer!
snippet.description:
Buy now on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/270450/

Disco Dodgeball is a first-person dodgeball sports shooter where you race unicycle robots around a dance club and pelt each other with explosive bouncy projectiles.
